# Bee-A-Hero live camera sources — one per line.
# Copy this file to `sources.txt` and list your cameras to enable live mode.
# Blank lines and lines starting with '#' are ignored.
#
# Accepted forms:
#   0                          local webcam / capture-device index
#   rtsp://user:pass@cam/stream IP camera (RTSP)
#   http://cam/video.mjpg      MJPEG/HTTP stream
#   /abs/path/to/feed.mp4      a file — useful to test the live path without hardware
#
# If sources.txt is absent or none of its cameras open, the pipeline falls back
# to the test videos in data/raw/Test_Video/.
